00026     SimAtom
00027     ========================================================================*/
00029 template <class T> class SimAtom {
00030     public:
00032         SimAtom(const T &elem = 0) : m_elem(elem) {}
00034         BOOLEAN operator ==(const SimAtom<T> &sim_elem) const {
00035             return (m_elem == sim_elem.m_elem);
00036         }
00038         BOOLEAN operator ==(const T &elem) const {
00039             return (m_elem == elem);
00040         }
00042         BOOLEAN operator <(const SimAtom<T> &sim_elem) const {
00043             return (m_elem < sim_elem.m_elem);
00044         }
00046         BOOLEAN operator <(const T &elem) const {
00047             return (m_elem < elem);
00048         }
00049 
00051         const T& Get() const { return (m_elem); }
00053         void Clear(UINT8 set = 0x00) { memset(&m_elem, set, sizeof(T)); }
00055         BOOLEAN IsInvalid() const { return (m_elem == 0); }
00056 
00057     private:
00058         T m_elem;
00059 };
